MRKLEE - Modern Right-reKursive Language for Everyday Expression
a programming language by Hunter James

Main Features:
- line ends are notated by exclamation points
- to print,the command "yell" is used
- "if...go"
- "funky" definitions
- "record" to return
- '#' signifies comments

program
    : function_def block
    | function_def block program

function_def
    : FUNKY ID OPAREN zero_param_list CPAREN

zero_param_list
    : param_list
    | EMPTY

param_list
    : var_dec
    | var_dec COMMA param_list

var_dec
    : VAR ID

block
    : OBRACE statement_list CBRACE

statement_list
    : statement
    | statement statement_list

statement
    : if_statement
    | while_loop
    | print_command
    | var_def
    | block
    | unary EXCLAMATION
    | return_statement

if_statement
    : IF expr GO block
    | IF expr GO block alt_if_statement

alt_if_statement
    : or_if_statement
    | if_none_statement
    | EMPTY

or_if_statement
    : OR IF expr GO block alt_if_statement

if_none_statement
    : IFNONE block

expr
    : unary check_value
    | unary op
    | unary

unary
    : STRING
    | INTEGER
    | REAL
    | CHAR
    | id_statement
    | LAMBDA OPAREN zeroParamList CPAREN block

id_statement
    : ID
    | ID function_call
    | ID assignment

function_call
    : OPAREN zero_arg_list CPAREN

zero_arg_list
    : arg_list
    | EMPTY

arg_list
    : expr
    | expr COMMA arg_list

check_value
    : LESS_THAN unary
    | LESS_EQUALS unary
    | GREATER_THAN unary
    | GREATER_EQUALS unary
    | EQUAL_TO unary
    | NOT_EQUAL_TO unary

op
    : PLUS unary
    | MINUS unary
    | TIMES unary
    | BY unary
    | ASSIGN unary

while_loop
    : WHILE expr block

print
    : YELL OPAREN print_item CPAREN EXCLAMATION

print_item
    : DOUBLE_QUOTE STRING DOUBLE_QUOTE
    | expr
    | unary

var_def
    : var_dec ASSIGN expr EXCLAMATION

assignment
    : ASSIGN expr

return_statement
    : RECORD expr EXCLAMATION


































